00031 Color3 Color3::lookupColor(const String& name)
00032 {
00033   // check for some common colors to avoid lookup
00034   if (name == "black") return gfx::Color3(0,0,0);
00035   if (name == "white") return gfx::Color3(1,1,1);
00036   if (name == "red") return gfx::Color3(1,0,0);
00037   if (name == "green") return gfx::Color3(0,1,0);
00038   if (name == "blue") return gfx::Color3(0,0,1);
00039 
00040   
00041   for(Int i=0; ; i++) {
00042     ColorDatabaseEntry& e(colorDatabase[i]);
00043     if ( (e.r==0) && (e.g==0) && (e.b==0) ) break; // black serves as list sentinal
00044     if (name == e.name) return Color3( Real(e.r)/255.0, Real(e.g)/255.0, Real(e.b)/255.0 ); 
00045   }
00046   throw std::invalid_argument(Exception("color with name "+name+" not in database"));
00047 }
